013package org.apache.juneau.reflect;
014
015/**
016 * Identifies possible modifiers on classes, methods, fields, and constructors.
017 *
018 * <ul class='seealso'>
019 * </ul>
020 */
021public enum ReflectFlags {
022
023   /** PUBLIC */
024   PUBLIC,
025
026   /** NOT_PUBLIC */
027   NOT_PUBLIC,
028
029   /** PROTECTED */
030   PROTECTED,
031
032   /** NOT_PROTECTED */
033   NOT_PROTECTED,
034
035   /** STATIC */
036   STATIC,
037
038   /** NOT_STATIC */
039   NOT_STATIC,
040
041   /** MEMBER */
042   MEMBER,
043
044   /** NOT_MEMBER */
045   NOT_MEMBER,
046
047   /** INTERFACE */
048   INTERFACE,
049
050   /** CLASS */
051   CLASS,
052
053   /** HAS_PARAMS */
054   HAS_PARAMS,
055
056   /** HAS_NO_PARAMS */
057   HAS_NO_PARAMS,
058
059   /** DEPRECATED */
060   DEPRECATED,
061
062   /** NOT_DEPRECATED */
063   NOT_DEPRECATED,
064
065   /** ABSTRACT */
066   ABSTRACT,
067
068   /** NOT_ABSTRACT */
069   NOT_ABSTRACT,
070
071   /** TRANSIENT */
072   TRANSIENT,
073
074   /** NOT_TRANSIENT */
075   NOT_TRANSIENT
076}
